data.description: Looking for a home with plenty of space in the perfect place?!!! Look no further this two story home has 3 bedrooms 2 full bath and Laundry all on upper level, 1/2 bath on lower level for guest. Nice private backyard for the kiddos and pets. Beautiful eat-in kitchen with island for family meals, with separate dining room. Spacious Master Bedroom, with additional space with window for sit-in area or office space, also nice size walk-in closet. Home also offers extra storage space in shed  that stays with home in backyard.
